    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_01-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "今回の仕事は、うちをご指名って聞いて\n楽しみにして来ました。どんなお仕事なんです？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard this job specifically requested me‚\nso I’ve been really looking forward to it! What kind of job is it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.8666674296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "京都の人気ラーメンチェーン店の『極烙拉麺』から\nイベントと、広告への出演依頼だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s from a popular Kyoto ramen chain‚ “Gokuraku Ramen.”\nThey want you for an event and an advertisement.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.8000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.8543537456
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_01-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……えぇっ！　本当ですか！？\nうち、極烙拉麺さんの大ファンなんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? …Ehhh!? Really!?\nI’m a huge fan of Gokuraku Ramen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.2333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_01-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "特に、こってり味のラーメンはクセになるんです～\n京都にいた頃は常連でした。それで、イベントって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially their rich‚ thick broth—it’s totally addictive~!\nI used to be a regular when I lived in Kyoto! So‚ what’s the event?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2739415876,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 47.1333340962
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_12_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "『東京ラーメンパレード』というラーメンの祭典だ\nそこで、極烙拉麺さんが新作を発表するらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a ramen festival called the “Tokyo Ramen Parade.”\nThey’re set to unveil a brand-new ramen there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.2000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
